p_{a,t}^{ucD}=\underbrace{\left\{ \frac{\partial f_{a,t}}{\partial D_{a,t}}+\frac{1}{1+\overline{r}_{t+1}^{B}}\frac{\partial f_{a+1,t+1}}{\partial D_{a,t}}-\frac{1+\overline{r}_{t+1}^{D}}{1+\overline{r}_{t+1}^{B}}+\frac{\psi_{t+1}^{Risk}}{1+\overline{r}_{t+1}^{B}}\right\} }_{\text{User-cost of \ensuremath{D_{j,a,t}} measured at time t in nominal units.}}
