\left(1+\overline{r}_{t+1}^{B}\right)p_{a,t}^{ucD}=\left(1+\overline{r}_{t+1}^{B}\right)\left(1-\mu_{a,t}\right)p_{t}^{D}-\left(1+\overline{r}_{t+1}^{D}\right)+\left(1+\overline{r}_{t+1}^{B}\right)\psi_{t+1}^{Risk}+
\]

\end_inset


