\left\{ \left(1+r_{t+1}^{mort}\right)\mu_{t}+\tau_{t+1}^{W}+x_{t+1}-\frac{p_{t+1}^{D}}{p_{t}^{D}}\left(1-\delta_{t+1}^{d}\right)-\alpha_{t+1}^{Land}\right\} p_{t}^{D}
\]

