status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
In DREAM pensions are gender specific.
 As each generation in MAKRO is a cohort average, we sum pension contributions
 paid by men and women into their pension funds, as well as pensions received
 by men and women.
\end_layout

\end_inset

) and aggregates into three pension types indexed 
\begin_inset Formula $i\in\{'Alder','Kap','PensX'\}$
\end_inset

: 1) pensions that have already been taxed (primarily 
