\[
X_{a,t}^{Beq}\equiv\left(1-\tau_{t+1}^{Beq}\right)\frac{B_{a,t}+p_{t}^{D}\left(1-\mu_{a,t}\right)D_{a,t}+V_{a,t}^{PensionB}}{p_{t+1}^{c}}-\xi^{0}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
and the utility associated with bequests is scaled with 
\begin_inset Formula $\xi_{a,t}^{Beq}$
\end_inset

 .
