\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Similarly to the bequest function, the utility of wealth is
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
V_{a,t}^{Wealth}=\xi_{a,t}^{Wealth}\frac{\left[X_{a,t}^{Wealth}\right]^{1-\eta}}{1-\eta}\label{eq:v_beq-1-1}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

where the elasticity 
\begin_inset Formula $\eta$
\end_inset

