\begin_inset Formula $X^{Wealth}$
\end_inset

, as
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
X_{a,t}^{Wealth}\equiv\frac{B_{a,t}+p_{t}^{D}\left(1-\mu_{a,t}\right)D_{a,t}+V_{a,t}^{PensionW}}{p_{t+1}^{c}}-\xi^{0}
\]

\end_inset

with the difference relative to bequests being the absence of the inheritance
